<l>ceṟivaṟintu cīrmai payakku maṟivaṟin</l>
<l>tāṟṟi ṉaṭaṅkap peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Knowing integrity, it will yield excellence, if knowing knowledge</l>
<l>one attain to restraint upon the righteous path.</l>
